Insider Activity


Individual




Richard L. Gelfond



Dr. Richard L. Gelfond is Chairman at Imax China Holdings, Inc., Chief Executive Officer & Director at IMAX Corp., Chairman at Stony Brook Foundation, Inc., and a Member at Academy of Motion Picture Arts & Sciences. He is on the Board of Directors at IMAX Corp., Brookhaven Science Associates LLC, Brookhaven National Laboratory, and The Atlantic Council of the United States.
Dr. Gelfond was previously employed as Vice Chairman by New-York Historical Society.
He received his undergraduate degree from Stony Brook University and a doctorate degree from the Northwestern University School of Law.



